<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.8.1">
<l>ārā vamutē yaṭiyē ṉuṭala niṉpā laṉpāyē</l>
<l>nīrā yalaintu karaiya vurukkukiṉṟa neṭumālē</l>
<l>cīrār cennel kavari vīcuñ ceḻunīrt tirukuṭantai</l>
<l>yērār kōlan tikaḻak kiṭantāy kaṇṭē ṉemmāṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O never-sating ambrosia, you on whom is the love of me, your servant’s body,</l>
<l>Tall Māl who make [me] melt so that I shake [and] cry, becoming water,</l>
<l>I have seen you lie, our lord, while [your] form that is full of beauty shimmers</l>
<l>In Tirukuṭantai with rich waters that fling chowries into the excellent red paddy.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
